title: Reading Night Reminder
publishedOn: 2026-09-01
summary: Families are invited to spend a few minutes reading together and talk about the story afterward.
featured: false
---

Try to make reading time feel relaxed.

Students can read aloud, listen to a family member read, or retell the story afterward.

The goal is to build comfort, not pressure.
